response.overview: "GOLF - Tee Shot" is the story of naked ambition. Rocko will go to any lengths to buy and sell his way up the social ladder. He thinks he likes the finer things in life, where a sardine sandwich is the height of sophistication. Wash it down with a fine Vintage Cider and he feels invincible. And if you don't want to play ball, well things may go a little out of bounds. Nothing, and I mean nothing and no one, will stand in the way of Rocko becoming Captain of the local Golf Club.
response.title: GOLF - Tee Shot
